            "format": "basic_html",
            "processed": "<p><strong>FishFeats: napari plugin to perform quantification of multimodal labeling at the single-cell level in 3D tissues.</strong></p><p>FishFeats allows to perform together in the same pipeline several analysis to quantify epithelia cells in 3D tissue, analysing cell morphology, nuclei, immuno-staining or RNA expression. The plugin allows flexibility to let the user choose the relevant step for a specific biological question.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
            "summary": "",
            "value": "<p><strong>FishFeats: napari plugin to perform quantification of multimodal labeling at the single-cell level in 3D tissues.</strong></p><p>FishFeats allows to perform together in the same pipeline several analysis to quantify epithelia cells in 3D tissue, analysing cell morphology, nuclei, immuno-staining or RNA expression. The plugin allows flexibility to let the user choose the relevant step for a specific biological question.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"
